---
// Korean variant of LinterDemo.astro.
// Terminal output stays English — it's literal CLI stdout.
---

<section class="linter section" aria-labelledby="linter-title">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <h2 id="linter-title" class="linter__title">린터를 실행하세요.</h2>
    <p class="linter__intro">
      방금 본 명세에 <code>specscore lint</code>를 실행해 보세요.
      결과는 다음과 같습니다.
    </p>

    <div
      class="linter__terminal"
      role="img"
      aria-label="specscore lint 터미널 출력: R1과 R2는 녹색 체크로 통과하고, R3은 빨간색 표시와 수정 가능한 오류 메시지로 실패합니다."
    >
<pre class="terminal"><span class="prompt">$</span> specscore lint checkout/apply-discount.md

  checkout/apply-discount.md
    <span class="mark-pass">✓</span> R1  Single-code limit
    <span class="mark-pass">✓</span> R2  Code validity
    <span class="mark-fail">✗</span> R3  Discount application
         <span class="dim">AC-3:18</span>  ambiguous AC — "higher-of rule" doesn't specify the tiebreaker
                  <span class="dim">expected:</span> concrete tie-break behavior, or reference to a defined rule
                  <span class="dim">fix:</span>      specify "higher discount wins; if tied, site-wide promotion wins"

  <span class="dim">1 of 3 requirements failing</span>
  <span class="dim">exit 1</span></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .linter { background: var(--cream); }
  .linter__title {
    font-size: var(--fs-h2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .linter__intro {
    color: var(--mid-ink);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
  }
  .linter__intro code {
    background: var(--cream-2);
    padding: 0.05em 0.35em;
    border-radius: 2px;
    font-size: 0.92em;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .linter__terminal {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3);
  }
</style>
